<paragraph id="789EAE7863145C7E9E64D79FB576F7BA" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">Very characteristic are the solitary, very shortly pedunculate flowers, the gradually widened flared corolla and the long, narrow sepals.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="D70823BFB7C2652A6BC798E21915B0BE" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">• Species 255-257 (and more distantly 258) form a small clade of closely related species.</paragraph>
